import React from 'react' import logo from './images/logo.svg' import { FaBars } from 'react-icons/fa' import {useGlobalContext} from './context' const Navbar = () => { const {openSidebar,openSubmenu,closeSubmenu} = useGlobalContext() const displaySubmenu = (e)=>{ e.preventDefault() openSubmenu() } return
} export default Navbar
